quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  68,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  68,1,noon. qalam ki aur jo ( ahal qalam ) likhte hain is ki qasam
  68,2,ke ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum apne perwar-digaar ke fazl se deewany nahi ho
  68,3,aur tumahray liye be intahaa ajar hai
  68,4,aur ikhlaq tumahray bohat ( aali ) hain
  68,5,so anqareeb tum bhi dekh lau ge aur yeh ( kafir ) bhi dekh len ge
  68,6,ke tum mein se kon deewana hai
  68,7,tumhara perwar-digaar is ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo is ke raste se bhatak gaya aur un ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo seedhay rastay par chal rahay hain
  68,8,to tum jhutlanay walon ka kaha nah maanna
  68,9,yeh log chahtay hain ke tum narmi ikhtiyar karo to yeh bhi naram ho jaien
  68,10,aur kisi aisay shakhs ke kahe mein nah aajana jo bohat kasmain khanay wala zaleel auqaat hai
  68,11,ta'an aamaiz ishartein karne wala chughlian liye phirnay wala
  68,12,maal mein bukhal karne wala hadd se barha howa badkaar
  68,13,sakht khoo aur is ke ilawa bud-zaat hai
  68,14,is sabab se ke maal aur betay rakhta hai
  68,15,jab is ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to kehta hai ke yeh aglay logon ke afsaanay hain
  68,16,hum anqareeb is ki naak par daagh lagayen ge
  68,17,hum ne un logon ki isi terhan azmaish ki hai jis terhan baagh walon ki azmaish ki thi. jab unhon ne kasmain kha kha kar kaha ke subah hotay hotay hum is ka mewa toar len ge
  68,18,aur Insha allah nah kaha
  68,19,so woh abhi so hi rahay they ke tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se ( raton raat ) is par aik aafat phir gayi
  68,20,to woh aisa hogaya jaisay kati hui khaiti
  68,21,jab subah hui to woh log aik dosray ko pukarnay lagey
  68,22,agar tum ko kaatna hai to apni khaiti par saweray hi ja pohncho
  68,23,to woh chal parre aur aapas mein chupkay chupkay kehte jatay they
  68,24,aaj yahan tumahray paas koi faqeer nah anay paye
  68,25,aur koshish ke sath saweray hi ja puhanche ( goya khaiti par ) Qadir hain
  68,26,jab baagh ko dekha to ( weraan ) kehnay lagey ke hum rasta bhool gay hain
  68,27,nahi balkay hum ( bur-ghashta naseeb ) be naseeb hain
  68,28,aik jo unn mein Farzana tha bola kekiya mein ne tum se nahi kaha tha ke tum tasbeeh kyun nahi karte ?
  68,29,( tab ) woh kehnay lagey ke hamara perwar-digaar pak hai be shak hum hi qasoorwar they
  68,30,phir lagey aik dosray ko ro Dur ro malamat karne
  68,31,kehnay lagey haae shamat hum hi hadd se barh gay they
  68,32,umeed hai ke hamara perwar-digaar is ke badlay mein hamein is se behtar baagh inayat kere hum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se rujoo laatay hain
  68,33,( dekho ) azaab yun hota hai. aur akhirat ka azaab is se kahin barh kar hai. kash! yeh log jantay hotay
  68,34,parhaiz garon ke liye un ke perwar-digaar ke haan Nemat ke baagh hain
  68,35,kiya hum farma-bardaron ko na-farmanoon ki taraf ( nematon se ) mahroom kar dein ge ?
  68,36,tumhekiya hogaya hai kaisi tjoyzin karte ho ?
  68,37,kiya tumahray paas koi kitaab hai jis mein ( yeh ) parhte ho
  68,38,ke jo cheez tum pasand karo ge woh tum ko zaroor miley gi
  68,39,ya tum ne hum se kasmain le rakhi hain jo qayamat ke din taq chali jayen gi ke jis shai ka tum hukum karo ge woh tumahray liye haazir hogi
  68,40,un se pucho ke un mein se is ka kon zimma laita hai ?
  68,41,kiya ( is qoul mein ) un ke aur bhi shareek hain? agar yeh sachey hain to apne sharikon ko laa samnay karen
  68,42,jis din pindli se kapra utha diya jaye ga aur kufar sjday ke liye bulaye jayen ge to sajda nah kar saken ge
  68,43,un ki ankhen jhuki hui hon gi aur un par zillat chhaa rahi hogi halaank pehlay ( uss waqt ) sjday ke liye bulatay jatay they jab ke sahih o salim they
  68,44,to mujh ko is kalaam ke jhutlanay walon se samajh lainay do. hum un ko aahista aahista aisay tareeq se pakren ge ke un ko khabar bhi nah hogi
  68,45,aur mein un ko mohlat diye jata hon meri tadbeer quwwat hai
  68,46,kiya tum un se kuch ajar mangte ho ke un par tawwan ka boojh par raha hai
  68,47,ya un ke paas ghaib ki khabar hai ke ( usay ) likhte jatay hain
  68,48,to apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke intzaar mein sabr kiye raho aur machhli ( ka luqmah honay ) walay Younis ki terhan raho na ke unhon ne ( khuda ) ko puraka aur woh ( gham o ) ghusse mein bharay hue they
  68,49,agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki meharbani un ki yavri nah karti to woh chtil maidan mein daal diye jatay aur un ka haal ab-tar hojata
  68,50,phir perwar-digaar ne un ko bargzida karkay naiko karon mein karliya
  68,51,aur kafir jab ( yeh ) nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) suntay hain to yun lagtay hain ke tum ko apni nigahon se phsla den ge aur kehte yeh to deewana hai
  68,52,aur ( logo ) yeh ( quran ) ahal aalam ke liye nasiyaat hai
